<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>semifly</title><link>http://localhost:1313/</link><description>semifly website</description><generator>Hugo 0.140.0 &amp; FixIt v0.3.16</generator><language>zh-CN</language><managingEditor>1024@semifly.top (semifly)</managingEditor><webMaster>1024@semifly.top (semifly)</webMaster><copyright>本站内容采用 CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 国际许可协议。</copyright><lastBuildDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 16:03:03 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="http://localhost:1313/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>安装主题</title><link>http://localhost:1313/documentation/installation/</link><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 10:29:25 +0800</pubDate><author>1024@semifly.top (semifly)</author><guid>http://localhost:1313/documentation/installation/</guid><category domain="http://localhost:1313/categories/documentation/">Documentation</category><description>&lt;p>只需几个步骤即可为你的 Hugo 站点安装 &lt;strong>FixIt&lt;/strong> 主题。&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>在 &lt;code>hugo.toml&lt;/code> 中配置默认主题为 FixIt，例如 &lt;code>theme = &amp;quot;FixIt&amp;quot;&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>通过以下其中一种方式安装主题&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;h2 id="先决条件" class="heading-element">&lt;span>先决条件&lt;/span>
 &lt;a href="#%e5%85%88%e5%86%b3%e6%9d%a1%e4%bb%b6" class="heading-mark">
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true">&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z">&lt;/path>&lt;/svg>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>由于 Hugo 提供的便利性，&lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">Hugo&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>&lt;/a> 可能是此主题的唯一依赖项。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>尽管不是在所有情况下都需要，但是在使用 Hugo 时通常会使用 &lt;a href="https://git-scm.com/"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">Git&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>&lt;/a>、&lt;a href="https://go.dev/"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">Go&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>&lt;/a>、&lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/hugo-pipes/transpile-sass-to-css/#dart-sass"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">Dart Sass&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>&lt;/a> 和 &lt;a href="https://nodejs.org/"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">Node.js&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>&lt;/a>。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Git 用于：&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>从源代码构建 Hugo&lt;/li>
&lt;li>使用 &lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/hugo-modules/"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">Hugo 模块&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>&lt;/a> 功能&lt;/li>
&lt;li>将主题安装为 Git 子模块&lt;/li>
&lt;li>从本地 Git 存储库访问 &lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/variables/git/"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">提交信息&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>使用 &lt;a href="https://cloudcannon.com/"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">CloudCannon&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>&lt;/a>、&lt;a href="https://pages.cloudflare.com/"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">Cloudflare Pages&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>&lt;/a>、&lt;a href="https://pages.github.com/"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">GitHub Pages&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>&lt;/a>、&lt;a href="https://docs.gitlab.com/ee/user/project/pages/"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">GitLab Pages&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>&lt;/a> 和 &lt;a href="https://www.netlify.com/"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">Netlify&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>&lt;/a> 等服务托管你的站点&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>Go 用于：&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>从源代码构建 Hugo&lt;/li>
&lt;li>使用 Hugo 模块功能&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>Dart Sass 用于在使用 Sass 语言的最新功能时将 Sass 转译为 CSS。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Node.js 用于：&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>使用 FixIt CLI&lt;/li>
&lt;li>使用一些自动化工具，例如&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>请参考相关文档以获取安装说明：&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/installation/"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">Hugo&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>&lt;/a>（扩展版，v 或更高版本）&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://git-scm.com/book/en/v2/Getting-Started-Installing-Git"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">Git&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://go.dev/doc/install"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">Go&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;em>&lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/hugo-pipes/transpile-sass-to-css/#dart-sass"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">Dart Sass&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>&lt;/a>（尚未使用）&lt;/em>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://nodejs.org/en/download/"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">Node.js&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>&lt;/a>（v16.0.0 或更高版本）&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="manual" class="heading-element">&lt;span>手动安装&lt;/span>
 &lt;a href="#manual" class="heading-mark">
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true">&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z">&lt;/path>&lt;/svg>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>你可以下载主题的 &lt;a href="https://github.com/hugo-fixit/FixIt/releases"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">最新版本 &lt;i class="fa-regular fa-file-archive fa-fw" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>&amp;nbsp;.zip 文件&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>&lt;/a> 并将其解压到 &lt;code>themes&lt;/code> 目录中。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>要升级主题，请用新主题替换旧主题。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="git-clone" class="heading-element">&lt;span>Git 克隆&lt;/span>
 &lt;a href="#git-clone" class="heading-mark">
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true">&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z">&lt;/path>&lt;/svg>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>这种方式，只需将 &lt;a href="https://github.com/hugo-fixit/FixIt"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">FixIt&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>&lt;/a> 主题克隆到 &lt;code>themes&lt;/code> 目录中即可。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">git clone https://github.com/hugo-fixit/FixIt.git themes/FixIt&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>通过从存储库中拉取最新提交来升级主题。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">cd&lt;/span> themes/FixIt
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">git pull&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="git-submodule" class="heading-element">&lt;span>Git 子模块&lt;/span>
 &lt;a href="#git-submodule" class="heading-mark">
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true">&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z">&lt;/path>&lt;/svg>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;!-- markdownlint-disable-next-line no-bare-urls -->
&lt;a href="https://github.com/hugo-fixit/hugo-fixit-starter1/generate" title="一个基于 Git 子模块创建 Hugo FixIt 站点的快速启动模板。"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer" class="card-link">&lt;span class="cl-backdrop" style="--cl-bg-url: url(/images/fixit.min.svg);">&lt;/span>
 &lt;span class="cl-content">
 &lt;span class="cl-text">
