&lt;div class="details admonition tip open">
 &lt;div class="details-summary admonition-title">&lt;i class="icon fa-fw fa-regular fa-lightbulb" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>技巧&lt;i class="details-icon fa-solid fa-angle-right fa-fw" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>&lt;/div>
 &lt;div class="details-content">
 &lt;div class="admonition-content">以这种方式，无需要在 &lt;code>hugo.toml&lt;/code> 中配置 &lt;code>theme = &amp;quot;FixIt&amp;quot;&lt;/code>。&lt;/div>
 &lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;p>将 &lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/hugo-modules/"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">Hugo 模块&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>&lt;/a> 用于主题的最简单方法是将其导入配置中。请参阅 &lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/hugo-modules/use-modules/"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">使用 Hugo 模块&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>&lt;/a>。&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>初始化 Hugo 模块系统：&lt;code>hugo mod init github.com/&amp;lt;your_user&amp;gt;/&amp;lt;your_project&amp;gt;&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>导入主题：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-toml" data-lang="toml">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">module&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">]&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">[[&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">module&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">imports&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">]]&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">path&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;github.com/hugo-fixit/FixIt&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;p>要更新或管理版本，你可以使用 &lt;code>hugo mod get&lt;/code> 命令。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">8
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># 更新所有模块&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">hugo mod get -u
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># 更新所有模块及其依赖&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">hugo mod get -u ./...
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># 更新一个模块&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">hugo mod get -u github.com/hugo-fixit/FixIt
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># 获取特定版本（例如 v0.3.2, @latest, @master, @dev）&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">hugo mod get github.com/hugo-fixit/FixIt@v0.3.2&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
